OL,3,CMother wants to challenge conviction
OL,4,Cfor murdering five-year-old son
OL,6,FA mother who was convicted of
OL,7,Fmurdering her five-year-old son wants
OL,8,Fher case to be reviewed by the body
OL,9,Fwhich investigates potential
OL,10,Fmiscarriages of justice, an inquest
OL,11,Fhearing has been told.
OL,13,FAngharad Williamson was jailed for
OL,14,Flife in 2022 for the murder of her son
OL,15,FLogan Mwangi, alongside his stepfather
OL,16,FJohn Cole and teenager Craig Mulligan,
OL,17,Fwho was 14 at the time.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
