OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784229523
OL,3,CMother wants to challenge conviction
OL,4,Cfor murdering five-year-old son
OL,6,FLogan's body was discovered by police
OL,7,Fofficers in the River Ogmore in 2021.
OL,8,FA post-mortem examination found he had
OL,9,Fsuffered more than 56 injuries,
OL,10,Fdescribed as being similar to those
OL,11,Fexpected from a fall from great height
OL,12,For a high speed car crash.
OL,14,FWilliamson was jailed for life with a
OL,15,Fminimum term of 28 years in prison,
OL,16,FCole for life with a minimum term of
OL,17,F29 years, and Mulligan detained for a
OL,18,Fminimum of 15 years during a
OL,19,Fsentencing hearing in June 2022.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
