OL,3,CMother wants to challenge conviction
OL,4,Cfor murdering five-year-old son
OL,6,FA pre-inquest review was held at South
OL,7,FWales Central Coroners' Court on
OL,8,FWednesday. Logan's inquest has been
OL,9,Fset for November 2027 - more than six
OL,10,Fyears after his murder.
OL,12,FWilliamson, appearing via video link,
OL,13,Fwas represented in court by Tony
OL,14,FThompson, who told assistant coroner
OL,15,FDavid Regan that he was a former
OL,16,Fsenior police officer.
OL,18,FMr Thompson told the coroner: "I've
OL,19,Fbeen instructed by Angharad Williamson
OL,20,Fto review her conviction. I had no
OL,21,Fprevious involvement in the matter.
OL,26,@zD@_OU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784229523
OL,3,CMother wants to challenge conviction
OL,4,Cfor murdering five-year-old son
OL,6,F"I'm conducting a review of her
OL,7,Fconviction at her request, at not cost.
OL,9,F"The ultimate aim is to determine
OL,10,Fwhether there are sufficient grounds
OL,11,Fto submit an application to the
OL,12,FCriminal Cases Review Commission."
OL,14,FMr Thompson requested interested
OL,15,Fperson status ` giving him the right
OL,16,Fto participate during the inquest ` as
OL,17,Fhe said that the inquest and his
OL,18,Finvestigation are "closely related".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUtD@bO]zD@SOUzD@cO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
