FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784229523
OL,3,CMother wants to challenge conviction
OL,4,Cfor murdering five-year-old son
OL,6,FThe coroner told Mr Thompson and
OL,7,FWilliamson to submit a formal written
OL,8,Fapplication within four weeks.
OL,10,FDuring the hearing, Mr Regan said the
OL,11,Finquest would be heard by a coroner
OL,12,Fand not by a jury.
OL,14,FIt will examine events dating back to
OL,15,FAugust 2020, when Logan was taken to
OL,16,Fhospital with injuries to his body.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
