FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784229523
OL,3,CMother wants to challenge conviction
OL,4,Cfor murdering five-year-old son
OL,6,FMr Regan said the scope of the inquest
OL,7,Fwill include the "investigation,
OL,8,Fassessment, management and
OL,9,Fsafeguarding" of Logan, including when
OL,10,FMulligan was reintroduced to his home
OL,11,Fshortly before his death.
OL,13,FThere will also be consideration of
OL,14,Fthe circumstances in which Logan was
OL,15,Ffound unresponsive on July 31 2021 and
OL,16,Fthe cause of his death.
OL,18,FLegal representatives for South Wales
OL,19,FPolice, Bridgend County Borough
OL,20,FCouncil and Cwm Taf Morgannwg Health
OL,21,FBoard also joined the hearing.
OL,26,@oD@ROUqD@MO]
